 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing poker is the turkish##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the person playing chess is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
