.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, motorbike-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, taxi, helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the malaysian and the person driving the motorbike##2
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the tram is between the thai and the person driving the helicopter##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person who's hobby is motorbike-climbing is the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the american is the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person who's hobby is motorbike-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | motorbike-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Transport   | helicopter | tram    | motorbike    | jet-ski       | taxi         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 